Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.23,0:01:52.75,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Hado Number 33:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.35,0:01:54.25,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Sokatsui!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:20.52,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:23.06,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,My bad. I got caught off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:24.28,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:28.56,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You could’ve easily dodged \Nthat attack with Flash Step.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:31.84,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I could manage \Nwithout using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:34.42,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, you nearly \Ngot yourself killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:36.49,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, your…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:40.59,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:42.11,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:45.07,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,It’s you guys again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.07,0:02:46.07,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Imoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:48.05,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,Who’re you calling Imoyama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:49.33,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,The name’s Kurumadani!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:51.16,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,Ku-ru-ma-da-ni!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:52.72,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Does it really matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:53.99,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:55.24,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:59.77,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t do anything else \Nwithout my permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:01.11,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.17,0:03:04.73,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh please, Imoyama…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:07.69,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,He does have a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:10.41,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he is my replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:14.08,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to overdo yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:16.74,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:29.95,B2,MOTHER,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:31.44,B2,MOTHER,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:36.54,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s nice, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:40.61,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to live a peaceful \Nand ordinary life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.19,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:59.70,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So this guy’s excuse was because \Nhe saw it yesterday on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:02.05,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:06.51,B2,MIZUIRO,0000,0000,0000,,As always, your story \Nhas no point, Keigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:07.60,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:09.99,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That’s harsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:13.19,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying to liven up the mood \Nof our after-lunch conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:14.84,B2,MIZUIRO,0000,0000,0000,,After? You’re still eating…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:16.87,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not my point!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:19.44,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,-Why are you always like this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:18.52,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,-Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:23.95,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:25.91,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:29.96,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Is Ichigo still doing \Nthat thing of his?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:31.90,B2,MIZUIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:33.12,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You’re okay with all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:34.67,B2,MIZUIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.32,B2,MIZUIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:43.83,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:52.59,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:54.22,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:57.31,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…just taking a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:05:00.03,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What about you? You were \Nstaying pretty late today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:01.76,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Had to make up for the \Nclasses I missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:05.50,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I had to skip school for a \Nwhile to deal with Aizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:07.28,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:10.13,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Your job is to be a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:11.29,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:14.23,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rukia…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:15.50,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:17.59,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going \Nto be staying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:20.50,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,That’s none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:22.91,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:26.24,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You’re freeloading \Nat my place, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:30.47,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Your family said I could \Nstay as long as I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.60,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That was Yuzu and my old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:41.11,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll go back when my mission is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:42.35,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:45.77,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn’t we be hurrying home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:49.67,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister was excited about \Nmaking curry for dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:51.08,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:54.70,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu asked me to pick up some pickles \Nfor the side on my way home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:56.75,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Then you’d better get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:58.87,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:01.54,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You fool…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:10.68,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:11.89,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:24.53,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Now’s my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:29.70,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Damn… Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:50.64,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:57.65,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Ishida.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:01.49,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Why’d you struggle \Nagainst a mere Hollow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:03.99,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I said thanks, didn’t I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:08.70,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we scared you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.19,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:11.92,B2,CHILD'S SPIRIT,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:14.20,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Another Hollow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:15.94,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Sure are a lot tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:17.60,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let’s go, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:18.86,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:20.83,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida and I will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:23.12,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:24.82,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,You’re such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:26.97,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to just \Nleave this kid alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:30.05,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You can come after you perform \NKonso on this spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:31.78,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.85,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki, about Kurosaki’s \NSpiritual Pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.65,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I know. It’s reaching its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:51.73,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,The Spiritual Pressure that was \Nrestored using the Mod Soul was temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:55.20,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,His Spirit Energy is dropping rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:58.50,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,He’s probably unable to \Ndo even a Flash Step…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:01.86,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Then why do you allow Kurosaki \Nto continue fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:03.15,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,In his condition, he’ll…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:04.25,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:06.31,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:09.52,B2,UKITAKE (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,I understand your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:15.30,B2,UKITAKE (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki…you need to keep \NIchigo from fighting any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:19.40,B2,RUKIA (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,But what about Ichigo's feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.85,B2,UKITAKE (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,I’m aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:26.09,B2,UKITAKE (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,However, he is losing his Spirit Energy \Nfar sooner than we had anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:27.86,B2,UKITAKE (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,It’s too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.56,B2,RUKIA (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.05,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:53.29,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Why’re you staring \Nblankly out into space?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:54.72,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:58.25,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You’ve been \Nacting strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.28,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,No I haven’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.73,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Then why won’t you \Nlook me in the face?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:05.58,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve been like \Nthat for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:21.21,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,There’s something you want \Nto tell me, isn’t there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:22.61,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:26.04,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It’s okay. You don’t \Nhave to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:27.03,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:29.60,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What’s with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:31.97,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,First you tell me to say it, \Nthen you tell me not to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:33.04,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:34.68,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:36.01,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Quit messing with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:38.22,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I apologized, didn’t I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:41.97,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve known each \Nother a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:45.54,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I can pretty much guess \Nwhat you’re thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:49.44,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a piece of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:52.44,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll hear what you have \Nto say before you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:53.53,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.93,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she’s here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:58.95,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,You’re late, Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:02.59,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.48,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:07.66,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t it obvious? It’s ice-skating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:11.09,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,No, what I meant was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:14.96,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You were staring at this \Nplace the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:20.49,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought you wanted \Nto go ice-skating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:21.61,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:26.43,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Dummy…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:27.71,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.15,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.81,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It gets really pretty here \Nduring springtime with
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,all the cherry blossoms in bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:36.40,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, we can just \Nask Byakuya and have
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:37.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,him show us cherry blossoms \Nanytime we want, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:41.07,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think my brother is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:44.41,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,So why’d you bring everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:47.37,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What? You don’t get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:49.88,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki! Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.33,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:53.08,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:54.25,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:55.41,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:56.80,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve never done this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.72,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way! Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:00.81,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:07.94,B2,MIZUIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Try relaxing a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:12.65,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:14.84,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no you don’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.48,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.66,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I’m going to let go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.32,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.72,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,How’s that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:32.33,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:34.92,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:52.14,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:55.03,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the only one stuck here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:57.89,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody looks like they’re \Nhaving so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:11:59.35,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:02.36,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sure no one would notice \Nif I get out for a bit…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:05.41,B2,CHILD,0000,0000,0000,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:07.29,B2,CHILD,0000,0000,0000,,This doll is moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:11.16,B2,MOTHER,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be silly. That’s impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:13.14,B2,CHILD,0000,0000,0000,,But it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:30.85,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It’s pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:34.60,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Why are there fireworks \Nat this time of year?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:37.15,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,A theme park opened recently nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:41.16,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,They do fireworks every \Nday at about this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:43.09,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,There’s a place like that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:45.56,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What? You didn’t know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:49.37,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not big, but it’s \Na pretty nice date spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:53.12,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Just the other day, I \Nwent there with Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:55.23,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:03.02,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It’s nice to spend time \Nlike this for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:04.77,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:16.19,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,See you! Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.10,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:24.78,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:27.86,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Coming from you, that was a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:31.11,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You just can’t come out \Nand compliment me, can you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:36.24,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, something’s \Nbeen bugging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:37.21,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:39.13,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That time…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:41.53,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know where I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:45.60,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I had lost control of myself back there,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:48.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so I should have been difficult \Nto recognize, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:51.57,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.71,0:13:52.56,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.14,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:03.32,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to when we first \Nmet, you became stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:11.78,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Your Spiritual Pressure \Nwent to a whole new level.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:20.29,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn’t change at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.31,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What’re you…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.21,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:30.98,B2,UKITAKE (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You need to keep Ichigo \Nfrom fighting any more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:33.03,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:34.77,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:37.71,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel its Spiritual Pressure \Nall the way over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:39.00,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a pretty big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:40.69,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:41.65,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:54.70,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.06,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It dodged me like I was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.03,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:10.68,B2,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no… His Spiritual Pressure’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.84,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Damn…not now…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:15.81,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.51,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:32.74,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I’m getting in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:36.54,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! Don’t say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:38.88,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:41.79,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,If you get hurt, then \NI’ll support you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:45.28,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,If you can’t move, then \NI’ll fight in your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:49.39,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re in pain, then \NI’ll bear your pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:52.13,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,We’re friends, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:57.28,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you’re right…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:02.66,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:03.96,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I’m okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:12.75,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia…can you stop its legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:15.91,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:24.57,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Dance, Sodenoshirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:34.76,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuginomai, Hakuren!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:48.27,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,This is my last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:49.78,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:16:59.34,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:01.25,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Getsuga…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:03.52,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,tensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:16.65,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:17.54,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.30,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Just barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:23.95,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you’re \Nalways going overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:27.37,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It’s like you just said…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:29.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, \NI’ll always be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:34.95,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So don’t hide stuff \Nthat you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:41.41,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You…knew about my mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:46.18,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I can sort of guess what the old \Nman and the others are thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:47.64,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:51.03,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve put you through \Na lot, haven’t I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:53.99,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:54.94,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:01.30,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:02.64,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:10.15,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I made you tag along \Nwith me until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:12.82,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t say that…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:17.29,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You…fool…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:22.30,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,We’re friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:23.85,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:25.26,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I know that…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:27.54,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Now, rest…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:39.47,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, you’re right…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:44.76,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, \Nwe won’t change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:03.66,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:05.49,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.36,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Is this my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:09.46,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:13.50,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! My powers…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:15.98,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:22.00,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Your body is going through the second \Nstage of Spiritual Pressure loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.11,0:19:26.75,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, your remaining Spiritual \NPressure will be gone, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:41.32,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:48.35,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it was about that time…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:56.82,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:18.55,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don’t sense any spirit presence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.19,0:20:26.53,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even Rukia’s presence is \Ngradually fading away…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:31.42,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really am…losing my powers…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:38.84,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,This is goodbye, Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.87,0:20:42.30,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Looks that way…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:48.59,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don’t make such a sad face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:53.58,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can’t see me, I’ll \Nstill be able to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:54.80,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:56.55,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn’t make me happy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:20:59.27,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,And I’m not making \Na sad face, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:18.25,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Give everybody…my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:19.68,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I will…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.15,0:21:32.48,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:49.28,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:23.10,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no more reason for me \Nto stay at Ichigo’s place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.10,0:23:25.01,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Then I’ll take you in!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:26.89,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,I just came up with a \Nnew design for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.89,0:23:29.06,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Let me cuddle him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.06,0:23:31.10,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t give up on this one, \Neven if it’s against you, Sado!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:33.53,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Don’t fight over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:34.85,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You’re both creeping me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.73,0:23:40.33,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, my life’s \Nbeen nothing but fighting…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:41.95,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Starting with the next episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:43.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to make the most \Nout of my high-school life!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.82,0:23:46.24,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,We still haven’t done \Nour sports festival…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.61,0:23:47.99,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,And I also want to do \Nthe cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.29,0:23:50.28,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and then there’s \Nthe class trip…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.59,0:23:55.09,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.09,0:23:57.16,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,You’re starting your last year in \Nhigh school with the next episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.16,0:23:58.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,-so make sure you have everything ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.77,0:23:58.46,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.97,0:23:59.77,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:03.03,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You’re kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.03,0:24:05.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,